overview.en: `I` token is an ecological token which is served for FO.COM, FO.COM is an one-stop integrated crowd-funding financing platform. `I` token can be used for voting of the projects and the development of the entire FO platform.
overview.zh: I币是服务于区块链领域的一站式众筹融资服务平台FO.COM的生态代币,用于项目的投票上线以及整个fo平台的发展运营。
